@chrisssj2

if you haven't already figured it out, here's a tip:

revert to that fresh install, and before you try to launch the game make sure you have anything like PeerBlock disabled.  The patcher will think the game is up to date if it can't accept incoming connections :(

For that matter, I haven't even successfully launched the game without disabling my Kaspersky as well.  I'll work on tweaking that for myself, but the main thing here is that you won't get very far with this if there are any limitations on your network traffic.
